# HolocronToolset

A PyQt5 application that can edit the files used by the KotOR game engine.

## Requirements

- Python 3

## Local Run

### Windows

Run from command line:

```
pip install -r requirements.txt
set PYTHONPATH=%cd%
python toolset/__main__.py
```

### Unix

Run from terminal:

```
pip install -r requirements.txt
PYTHONPATH=$PWD python toolset/__main__.py
```